@reflexes: Wish I had some english audio books to upload. I only have Harry Potter in english, but I think you can find all of them here if you are interested. If you have a specific book you want, maybe I can help you. I am a frequent visitor at the library and they have quite a few audio books in in english. Write here (or in any other of my new uploads) and tell me what books you want.
